data.description: Welcome home to this completely remodeled 4 sided brick home home on a crawl space, within walking distance to downtown Auburn. 3 bedroom 1 bath, open floorplan on almost a half acre lot with a large front and back yard.  Dining room / Kitchen combo with good natural lighting, and granite countertops. EVERYTHING IS less than 2 years old including roof, HVAC, Windows, Electrical, Plumbing, Paint, LVP Flooring & Appliances.
